    <item>
      <title>Ok. What do I get with SSGs?</title>
      <link>http://www.ericcarlisle.com/static-site-generators/07-what-do-i-get/</link>
      <pubDate>Tue, 14 Jun 2016 00:41:58 -0400</pubDate>
      
      <guid>http://www.ericcarlisle.com/static-site-generators/07-what-do-i-get/</guid>
      <description>&lt;ol class=&#34;big&#34;&gt;

  &lt;li&gt;Less dependencies - No server-side stack.&lt;/li&gt;

  &lt;li&gt;All you need is an HTTP server.&lt;/li&gt;

  &lt;li&gt;Works on GitHub pages (with some help).&lt;/li&gt;

  &lt;li&gt;Performance&lt;/li&gt;

  &lt;li&gt;Security&lt;/li&gt;

  &lt;li&gt;Content Source Control&lt;/li&gt;

&lt;/ol&gt;
</description>
